---

[TestGroupIntervalCheck/interval_above_5m_and_keep_firing_for_too_short - 1]
- description: interval above 5m and keep_firing_for too short
  content: |4

    - name: test
      interval: 10m
      rules:
      - alert: foo
        expr: foo > 0
        keep_firing_for: 5m
  output: |
    3 |   interval: 10m
                    ^^^ Using group interval > 5m will cause gaps in recording rule results and flapping alerts.
  problem:
    reporter: group/interval
    summary: interval too long
    details: ""
    diagnostics:
        - message: Using group interval > 5m will cause gaps in recording rule results and flapping alerts.
          firstcolumn: 1
          lastcolumn: 3
          kind: 0
    lines:
        first: 3
        last: 3
    severity: 1
    anchor: 0

